# Controllers

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](../../docs/ARCHITECTURE.md).

- Thin controllers: coordinate request/response; domain logic in models.
- Strong parameters on all writes.
- Explicit auth for events, friendships, participants, profile data.
- Do not run commands unless explicitly requested.

